What kind of situation is this?

106
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:45,870
Also, why is Jun-hee's mom
changing her attitude?

107
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:47,870
What should I say?

108
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:49,740
I'm flabbergasted.

109
00:06:51,370 --> 00:06:53,610
Anyway, what do you think?

110
00:06:53,670 --> 00:06:56,610
What's really important is

111
