113
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,160
What are you all talking about?

114
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:19,430
Thank you all for today.

115
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:21,440
Why don't we have brunch
at my hotel tomorrow?

116
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:24,570
Sounds great. I'd love that.

117
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:25,910
Okay then.

118
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:28,880
-See you.
-Bye.

119
00:07:29,610 --> 00:07:33,050
