It's just so unexpected.

125
00:07:50,330 --> 00:07:52,830
Is it some kind of strategic alliance?

126
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:54,770
Or

127
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:58,010
does she have something on you?

128
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:02,610
Even a rat would bite a cat when cornered.

129
00:08:02,810 --> 00:08:06,050
I'm just making sure
I don't get bitten by a rat.

130
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:12,490
