The mighty Nam Ji-seon...

131
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:16,360
Gosh. Just what is that woman?

132
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,460
Is he still doing this?

133
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:27,100
