134
00:08:30,810 --> 00:08:33,809
Jun-mo, open the door.

135
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:36,309
I took care of everything.

136
00:08:36,380 --> 00:08:38,250
You don't have to worry about anything.

137
00:08:38,309 --> 00:08:41,220
I told the school you were sick.

138
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:44,090
But tomorrow you're going to school, okay?

139
00:09:02,340 --> 00:09:04,870
