while I'm away.

140
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,710
He's more delicate than he lets on.

141
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:10,180
-If he does something again...
-Understood, ma'am.

142
00:09:16,020 --> 00:09:18,650
