It'll be uncomfortable here.

143
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:20,090
Just for a moment.

144
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:22,620
You should get going too.

145
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,690
Did you have dinner?

146
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:30,360
I apologize for causing you trouble.

147
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:39,140
