what can happen
when you trust others too easily.

172
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,080
Ma'am.

173
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:25,410
How are you feeling? Better?

174
00:11:25,810 --> 00:11:28,820
Yes. I'm okay now, thanks to you.

175
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:33,190
But no more of this, please.

176
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:36,660
-Pardon?
-Stop being so nosy.

177
00:11:44,570 --> 00:11:45,730
My goodness.

178
00:11:46,830 --> 00:11:49,000
