203
00:13:33,740 --> 00:13:35,640
I'm sorry, Mom.

204
00:13:37,410 --> 00:13:38,710
I see.

205
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:43,250
Mom, are you mad at me?

206
00:13:43,650 --> 00:13:46,590
No. Don't worry about it.

207
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:50,760
