you were so curious about me.

241
00:16:14,900 --> 00:16:16,000
What?

242
00:16:17,740 --> 00:16:19,840
No. Sorry.

243
00:16:19,940 --> 00:16:22,010
I apologize if I made you uncomfortable.

244
00:16:22,110 --> 00:16:24,180
