247
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,650
Because I ruled the ice back then.

248
00:16:32,050 --> 00:16:36,090
Center? No, wait.

249
00:16:37,290 --> 00:16:38,830
Goalie, right?

250
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:43,930
Well... I can be if you want.

251
00:16:44,770 --> 00:16:47,740
Then we should play sometime, right?

252
00:16:48,570 --> 00:16:49,740
Sure.

253
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:51,910
If you can skate.

254
00:16:52,470 --> 00:16:53,570
We'll see.

255
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:56,780
Relax, guys.

256
00:16:57,380 --> 00:16:58,810
