You knew everything, didn't you?

788
00:55:01,660 --> 00:55:04,300
Who are you? Do I know you?

789
00:55:04,930 --> 00:55:06,030
Answer your phone right now.

790
00:55:06,100 --> 00:55:08,030
[As your client, I need an answer.]

791
00:56:42,690 --> 00:56:44,630
"Family"?

792
00:56:47,370 --> 00:56:49,730
Who's your family? Who?

793
00:56:50,740 --> 00:56:51,870
Who?

794
00:56:52,700 --> 00:56:54,040
Who's your family?

795
00:57:23,970 --> 00:57:27,410
-Let's go.
-My dad does the same thing.

796
00:57:28,270 --> 00:57:29,510
I knew it.

797
00:57:38,180 --> 00:57:39,720
Did you finish early today?

798
00:57:40,790 --> 00:57:42,490
Mom, when did you get here?

799
00:57:42,720 --> 00:57:45,160
Ms. Song, can we play together today?

800
00:57:54,800 --> 00:57:58,270
What's wrong? Are you angry with me?

801
00:57:59,100 --> 00:58:02,870
No. It's just that you're so pretty.

802
00:58:03,540 --> 00:58:06,080
Jae-in, do you want to do
something fun with me?

803
00:58:06,140 --> 00:58:07,150
Yes.

804
00:58:07,280 --> 00:58:09,350
-Let's go.
-Come.

805
00:58:11,850 --> 00:58:13,350
-Mom!
-Hey, you're here.

806
00:58:13,420 --> 00:58:15,750
-Come.
-Did you have fun?

807
00:58:15,820 --> 00:58:17,760
-How was school?
-Mom!

808
00:58:18,820 --> 00:58:21,030
-Mom!
-Come here.

809
00:58:34,510 --> 00:58:36,040
She's late.

810
00:58:42,010 --> 00:58:46,380
She left right after class,
and I haven't seen her ever since then.

811
00:58:46,580 --> 00:58:48,420
But she never came out.

812
00:58:48,820 --> 00:58:51,320
Ma'am, please calm down.
I'm sure she'll be fine.

813
00:58:51,460 --> 00:58:54,260
We're checking the CCTV
in the entire school right now.

814
00:58:54,330 --> 00:58:55,760
We'll be able to find her in no time.

815
00:58:55,830 --> 00:58:57,030
I found her.

816
00:58:57,900 --> 00:58:59,430
She's leaving with someone.

817
00:59:12,080 --> 00:59:15,710
-Rock-paper-scissors.
-Rock-paper-scissors.

818
00:59:15,780 --> 00:59:18,280
-Rock-paper-scissors.
-Rock-paper-scissors.

819
00:59:18,350 --> 00:59:20,490
-Rock-paper-scissors.
-Rock-paper-scissors.

820
00:59:20,550 --> 00:59:22,120
[Jae-in's mom]

821
00:59:22,190 --> 00:59:25,160
-Rock-paper-scissors.
-Rock-paper-scissors.

822
00:59:35,700 --> 00:59:38,000
[Jae-in's mom]

823
00:59:38,070 --> 00:59:40,100
-Rock-paper-scissors.
-Rock-paper-scissors.

824
00:59:40,170 --> 00:59:42,140
-Play, or you lose.
-Rock-paper-scissors.

825
00:59:42,210 --> 00:59:43,980
[Jae-in's mom]

826
00:59:44,040 --> 00:59:46,110
-Play, or you lose.
-Rock-paper-scissors.

827
00:59:46,180 --> 00:59:48,610
How could you take my kid away
without saying anything to me?

828
00:59:49,780 --> 00:59:51,220
Let me talk to Jae-in right now.

829
00:59:52,650 --> 00:59:54,720
Are you sure
you still don't have anything to tell me?

830
00:59:56,320 --> 00:59:58,760
-Suit yourself.
-Hold on.

831
00:59:59,720 --> 01:00:01,130
I'll tell you.

832
01:00:01,560 --> 01:00:03,600
I'll tell you everything.
Please don't do this.

833
01:00:06,130 --> 01:00:09,200
Okay. I'll be right there.
Give me just a second.

834
01:00:09,430 --> 01:00:12,000
Ma'am, should we report to the police?

835
01:00:12,070 --> 01:00:14,840
We've found her, so you don't have to.
Thank you.

836
01:00:16,910 --> 01:00:17,980
Jae-in!

837
01:00:19,210 --> 01:00:20,480
Jae-in!

838
01:00:21,510 --> 01:00:23,080
Jae-in! Hwang Jae-in!

839
01:00:50,610 --> 01:00:53,480
Where's my daughter? Where is she?

840
01:00:54,950 --> 01:00:57,420
Don't worry. She's having a good time.

841
01:01:00,490 --> 01:01:01,720
So how do you feel?

842
01:01:02,520 --> 01:01:04,220
You stole my husband.

843
01:01:04,290 --> 01:01:06,560
And I stole your kid for a second.
How do you feel now?

844
01:01:07,760 --> 01:01:09,930
I was going to trust you no matter what.

845
01:01:10,560 --> 01:01:12,760
I thought you were the only person
who was kind to me.

846
01:01:12,830 --> 01:01:15,970
But what is this?
Was it your doing all along?

847
01:01:17,140 --> 01:01:18,440
The incident at the reception,

848
01:01:18,500 --> 01:01:20,510
the text, the flowers, all of them?

849
01:01:21,470 --> 01:01:23,240
How could you...

850
01:01:27,980 --> 01:01:29,880
Are you even human?

851
01:01:30,320 --> 01:01:32,080
How could you do that?

852
01:01:32,420 --> 01:01:35,350
It took you long enough,
Ms. Song Yeo-wool.

853
01:01:35,990 --> 01:01:38,490
Do you really not know why I did that?

854
01:01:39,520 --> 01:01:40,590
I know

855
01:01:41,930 --> 01:01:43,830
you killed him.

856
01:01:45,030 --> 01:01:46,400
Admit it.

857
01:01:54,540 --> 01:01:55,910
Is that why?

858
01:01:55,970 --> 01:01:57,180
He would

859
01:01:58,210 --> 01:02:00,510
never have killed himself like that.

860
01:02:03,280 --> 01:02:05,950
What exactly happened that day?

861
01:02:06,950 --> 01:02:08,020
Tell me.

862
01:02:08,820 --> 01:02:11,990
You and I both lost our husband.

863
01:02:12,160 --> 01:02:14,230
So why am I the only one?

864
01:02:18,160 --> 01:02:19,330
Get out of here right now,

865
01:02:19,400 --> 01:02:20,430
or I'll sue you for adultery

866
01:02:20,500 --> 01:02:22,400
and tell your daughter everything.

867
01:02:22,930 --> 01:02:26,040
You'll have to compensate me
for my mental and economic damages

868
01:02:26,400 --> 01:02:27,840
and be punished for blackmailing me.

869
01:02:27,910 --> 01:02:30,940
You and your daughter will never
be able to set foot here again.

870
01:02:31,840 --> 01:02:33,410
Are you telling me to leave?

871
01:02:34,510 --> 01:02:35,510
Why?

872
01:02:36,080 --> 01:02:38,320
What makes you so sure
that you were first?

873
01:02:39,580 --> 01:02:41,750
Does it ever occur to you
that you may not have been?

874
01:02:43,890 --> 01:02:45,960
-What?
-The painting in your study.

875
01:02:47,560 --> 01:02:48,630
The painting?

876
01:02:50,090 --> 01:02:52,260
[It was my first present to him.]

877
01:02:53,000 --> 01:02:55,000
[It was long before he met you.]

878
01:03:53,620 --> 01:03:54,930
That's nonsense.

879
01:03:55,530 --> 01:03:56,860
I was first.

880
01:03:56,930 --> 01:03:59,830
I'm not the one who stole him. You did.

881
01:04:01,930 --> 01:04:04,600
-You're being ridiculous.
-I'm sure you can't believe it.

882
01:04:05,240 --> 01:04:07,940
But Jae-in is his daughter.

883
01:04:08,110 --> 01:04:10,140
She was born before your son.

884
01:04:10,410 --> 01:04:12,580
She deserves more.

885
01:04:13,110 --> 01:04:16,980
I'll make sure she gets everything
she deserves but has never gotten.

886
01:04:18,250 --> 01:04:21,290
So if any of us has to leave,
it'll be you.

887
01:05:21,780 --> 01:05:24,420
[High Class]

888
01:05:25,180 --> 01:05:28,220
[Be careful.
I won't get stabbed in the back twice.]

889
01:05:28,490 --> 01:05:30,960
Do you think you're a match for me?

890
01:05:31,220 --> 01:05:33,160
Something's definitely going on,
don't you think?

891
01:05:33,220 --> 01:05:37,130
[In my line of work, a background check
on clients is a must.]

892
01:05:36,690 --> 01:05:37,700
[Letter of Resignation]

893
01:05:37,630 --> 01:05:39,260
I found quite some dirt on you.

894
01:05:39,330 --> 01:05:42,630
[Did An Ji-yong put you in this position?]

895
01:05:42,700 --> 01:05:44,640
[Now that I met you again,]

896
01:05:44,700 --> 01:05:46,670
[I'm becoming more convinced.]

897
01:05:46,440 --> 01:05:47,340
[An Ji-yong, Doh Jin-sol, Nam Ji-seon]

898
01:05:46,800 --> 01:05:50,140
[I have a feeling
that case wouldn't just end like that.]

